.TH Charco 1
.SH NAME
Charco
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBcharco\fP [\fBOPTIONS\fP]...
.SH DESCRIPTION
A character encoder.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-f\fP, \fB\-\-format\fP \fIformat\fP 
Select the output format. By default charco displays all formats.
.TP
\fB\-h\fP, \fB\-\-help\fP
Display this help text.
.TP
\fB\-\-usage\fP
Display the usage.
.TP
\fB\-v\fP, \fB\-\-version\fP
Display version information.
.SH EXAMPLES
.CW
$ charco ñ
  UTF-8: C3B1
  UTF-16: 00F1
  Unicode: U+00F1
  HTML: &#241;
  CSS: \00F1

$ charco -f html 愛
  HTML: &#24859;

$ charco -f utf8 我
  UTF-8: E68891
